            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "伊朗拒絕美國15點和平計劃,誓言繼續軍事行動",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ae3OCk7O4eJ3aGUyWhp_pA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_3_M_1440048334.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 伊朗國家電視台週三報導,伊朗已拒絕美國提出的15點和平計劃。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據伊朗國家電視台報導,伊朗已透過調解人向華盛頓傳達了拒絕立場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗媒體引述一名伊朗官員的話稱,伊朗的防禦性行動將持續進行,直至該國的條件得到滿足。該官員明確表示,結束衝突的首要條件是停止攻擊和暗殺行動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該官員稱,德黑蘭已透過一名地區調解人通知美國,伊朗將繼續進行自衛。該官員補充說,伊朗不會允許特朗普總統為衝突結束強加時間表。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-29652f2b-7054-342a-9cee-633a6faa5243-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據該官員表示,伊朗已審查了相關提案,並認為這些提案過於誇大。該官員表示,衝突將在伊朗選擇的時間結束,且僅在其條件得到滿足的情況下才會結束。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B15%E9%BB%9E%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E8%AA%93%E8%A8%80%E7%B9%BC%E7%BA%8C%E8%BB%8D%E4%BA%8B%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-151313094.html",
